## Success Criteria

1. Button component exists at `components/ui/button.tsx`
2. CSS variables --primary, --shadow-brutal, --border-brutal are defined
3. Fonts are loaded without errors
4. Dev server runs without errors after changes

## Risk Assessment

- **Low Risk:** Standard shadcn installation process
- **Low Risk:** CSS variables are additive, won't break existing styles
